    <div class="content"><p>And his Degenerate Earthicans - Especially Those Darn Africans - Dependent on the Largess From Space People could have come from a Jerry Pournelle novel circa 1974. Come to think of, so could the Space Heiress who gets handed a lot of power because she happens to be related to the late Lion of Mercury. And there's a bit in the book lifted from Cole and Cox's 1964 Islands in Space, possibly via Niven.</p>
