    <div class="content"><p>Of course the Hugos are measuring a worth, as judged by the presumably more sophisticated (or at least dedicated) fans who go to the worldcon.   It is an aggregate opinion, but in general works of greatness can and do impress those fans and win the award.   </p>
</div>
